<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Objednávka č. {$order->order_number}</title>
    <style>
        /* KLÍČOVÉ: mPDF vyžaduje DejaVu Sans pro správné zobrazení české diakritiky */
        body {
            font-family: 'DejaVu Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #1e293b;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .header-table {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header-table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3b82f6; /* Tvoje primární modrá */
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .document-title {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0f172a;
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Tabulka položek */
        .items-table {
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .items-table th {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #475569;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
        }

        .items-table td {
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .items-table th.right,
        .items-table td.right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table th.center,
        .items-table td.center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .total-row td {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0f172a;
            border-top: 2px solid #334155;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }

        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<table class="header-table">
    <tr>
        <td style="width: 50%;">
            <div class="company-name">Nette Blog Premium</div>
            <div>Provozovatel s.r.o.</div>
            <div>Ulice a číslo popisné 123</div>
            <div>100 00 Praha 1</div>
            <div>IČO: 12345678</div>
            <div>DIČ: CZ12345678</div>
        </td>
        <td style="width: 50%; text-align: right;">
            <div class="document-title">Potvrzení objednávky</div>
            <div><strong>Číslo objednávky:</strong> {$order->order_number}</div>
            <div>
                <strong>Vystaveno:</strong>
                {if $order->created_at}
                    {$order->created_at|date:'j. n. Y'}
                {else}
                    {date('j. n. Y')}
                {/if}
            </div>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<table style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <tr>
        <td style="width: 50%;">
            <div class="section-title">Odběratel</div>
            <strong>ID uživatele:</strong> #{$order->user_id}<br>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<table class="items-table">
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Položka</th>
        <th class="center" style="width: 15%;">Délka</th>
        <th class="right" style="width: 25%;">Cena celkem</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <tr>
        <td>
            <strong>{$order->item}</strong><br>
            <span style="color: #64748b; font-size: 9pt;">Aktivace VIP výhod na platformě Nette Blog</span>
        </td>
        <td class="center">
            {$order->duration_months} {if $order->duration_months == 1}měsíc{elseif $order->duration_months >= 2 && $order->duration_months <= 4}měsíce{else}měsíců{/if}
        </td>
        <td class="right">{$order->price|number:2, ',', ' '} Kč</td>
    </tr>

    <tr class="total-row">
        <td colspan="2" class="right">K úhradě celkem:</td>
        <td class="right">{$order->price|number:2, ',', ' '} Kč</td>
    </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<div style="margin-top: 50px; color: #475569;">
    <p>Děkujeme za vaši objednávku a podporu našeho projektu.</p>
    <p>Nejsme plátci DPH.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>